Buy It Now is streaming on Amazon FreeVee.
 
About Buy It Now: JB Smoove hosts a business competition where entrepreneurs get 90 seconds to pitch their product to an audience of potential customers: The 100. If The 100 like the product and price, then the entrepreneurs go to a panel of Amazon executives and celebrity entrepreneurs. The panel selects which products join Amazon’s exclusive Buy It Now Store and award one entrepreneur $20,000 each episode.

About Reacher: 
When retired Military Police Officer Jack Reacher is arrested for a murder he did not commit, he finds himself in the middle of a deadly conspiracy full of dirty cops, shady businessmen and scheming politicians. With nothing but his wits, he must figure out what is happening in Margrave, Georgia. The first season of Reacher is based on the international bestseller, Killing Floor by Lee Child.

The Pasta Queen is now streaming on Prime Video.

About The Pasta Queen: The Pasta Queen features NY Times bestselling author Nadia Caterina Munno, a descendant of an Italian pasta dynasty, who has racked up millions of followers on social. Come along as Nadia explores four regions of Italy highlighting their cuisine and ingredients. Back in her kitchen she will give step-by-step instructions on how to make Italian dishes, like a real Italian, that are just gorgeous!
